{"tid":527751,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【處理器漏洞】舊iPhone雪上加霜 升級iOS慢40%","createTime":"2018-01-13T04:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T17:10:04.000Z","uid":107023,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e634970cd48bbfce79d8a97709d63c7b1973182f","tid":527751,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"Apple日前推出iOS 11.2.2更新，主要是修復Safari及稱為「幽靈」（Spectre）的安全漏洞。不過更新推出後不久，陸續有網民發文表示，更新後iPhone的效能明顯下降。當中一名開發者前後共進行30次跑分，對比後證實其iPhone 6升級後，單核及多核跑分分別下降了41%及39%。不過，也有網民表示更新後有所提升。<br />\n<br />\n用家可以到App Store下載Geekbench 4，在升級前後都跑次分，就可以知道自己的iPhone在升級前後的變化。而Geekbench官方網站亦載有歷代iPhone的跑分，供用家參考對比。<br />\n<br />\n若此更新真的會大減iPhone的效能，對於未換電的舊iPhone來說，真的是雪上加霜了。<br />\n<br />\n文：梁志穎"},{"pid":"1e81fe361d2ccbd11189bc19b4a591de5cdaf089","tid":527751,"uid":141060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999d534117515e7291f95c860b9fe50a51e2a449","tid":527751,"uid":24211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"Apple係得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一撚再撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8751829750ec792498c87f160d099767dcc0665","tid":527751,"uid":151490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c046319e6b4ecde4e68162811ed31d472c7f57b","tid":527751,"uid":23677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過，也有網民表示更新後有所提升。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08caaf6eefa1930b19f9b5fdaf44f4a2ab16199","tid